据《中国社会报》2月10日报道，武汉市慈善总会于1月27日起分4批、累计27亿元抗疫善款上缴市财政。
The Wuhan Municipal Charity Association handed over 2.7 billion yuan in donations to the municipal treasury in four batches starting on January 27, the China Society for Social Welfare said.
报道称：“武汉市慈善总会作为民政部指定的五家接收捐赠的单位之一，主要负责接收捐款和通用物资。
"The Wuhan General Charity Federation is one of the five entities designated by the Ministry of Civil Affairs to receive donations and supplies," it said.
为做好慈善捐赠工作，武汉市民政局制定《武汉市新冠肺炎防控捐赠工作规程》，制发《关于加强新型肺炎防控社会捐赠工作管理的通知》，规范应对疫情的社会捐赠管理。
In order to do a good job in charitable donation, the Wuhan Civil Affairs Bureau formulated the Regulations on the Prevention and Control of New Crowded Pneumonia in Wuhan and issued the Notice on Strengthening the Management of Social Donations for the Prevention and Control of New Kinds of Pneumonia, regulating the management of social donations to deal with the epidemic.
1月23日以来，累计向社会发布接受捐赠款物情况的公告8期，捐赠款使用公告2期(涉及资金14.35亿元，含定向0.47亿元)，实现全额全程公开。
Since 23 January, eight issues of the cumulative notice of receipt of donations have been issued to the public, and two editions of the Notice on the Use of Donations (involving 1.435 billion yuan, including a targeted 47 million yuan) have been published in full.
截至2月2日12时，市慈善总会接收社会捐款共计30.226197亿元，并于1月27日起分4批上缴市财政，累计划转27亿元。
As at 12: 00 noon on February 2, the Municipal Charitable Association had received donations totalling 3,02261.97 million yuan and had transferred 2.7 billion yuan to the municipal treasury in four batches since January 27.
” 就此，北京致诚社会组织矛盾调处与研究中心执行主任何国科表示，此次新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情暴发后，所有捐赠人的捐赠目的，还是比较明确的，就是用于新冠肺炎的防控，慈善总会作为受赠主体，应将受赠的财产用于疫情防控。
In the wake of the outbreak of the new coronavirus pneumonia, the goal of all donors is clearly to prevent and control the new coronavirus pneumonia, and the General Association of Charities, as a grantee, should use the donated assets for disease prevention and control, the bureau said.
武汉市慈善总会根据指挥部要求上缴市财政的行为，从某种程度上来说是违背了捐赠人对捐赠资金如何使用的意愿。
The action of Wuhan General Association of Charity to turn over the city's financial resources according to the request of the headquarters is, to some extent, a violation of donors' willingness to use the donated funds.
北京荷风艺术基金会高级顾问夏彧歆认为，武汉市慈善总会应当按照募捐方案使用捐赠财产，如果需要变更，须经法定程序。
Xia or her, a senior adviser at the Beijing Lotus Foundations, believes that Wuhan Charity Association makes use of donated property in accordance with the fund-raising plan.
而目前在武汉市有关部门发布的各类公告、武汉市慈善总会公布的募捐方案中，均未提到社会捐赠款项要上缴武汉市财政。
However, none of the various announcements issued by the relevant departments in Wuhan and the fundraising plan announced by the Wuhan General Association of Charity did mention that the social donation should be turned in to Wuhan municipal finance.
上述两位专业人士均表示：在当前疫情防控和抗击的关键时期，相关部门应按照《慈善法》《公益事业捐赠法》等法律法规和与其配套的部门规章、规范性文件等，依法建立协调机制，提供需求信息，及时有序引导开展募捐和救助活动，并对捐赠款物使用情况依法严格监督。
Both professionals said that during the current critical period of epidemic prevention and combat, the relevant departments should establish a coordination mechanism in accordance with the Law on Charity, the Law on Donations to Public Welfare Enterprises and their accompanying departmental rules and normative documents, provide demand information, guide fund-raising and rescue activities in a timely and orderly manner, and strictly supervise the use of donations and materials in accordance with the law.
何国科 北京市致诚律师事务所律师，北京致诚社会组织矛盾调处与研究中心 执行主任 夏彧歆 北京荷风艺术基金会 高级顾问  访谈 《公益时报》：据《中国社会报》报道，武汉市慈善总会自1月27日起，将接收的捐款分4批上缴市财政，累计划转27亿元。
He Guoke is a lawyer at Zhicheng Law Firm in Beijing, and a senior adviser at the Zhicheng Social Organization in Beijing, Xia Yu-shin and Xin Xin, Executive Director of the Ho Feng Art Foundation in Beijing. Since January 27, the Association has handed in donations in four batches to the municipal treasury for a cumulative transfer of 2.7 billion yuan, the China Social Daily reported.
在你看来，这种操作是否符合捐赠人意愿?何国科：判断是否违反捐赠人的意愿，首先要明确捐赠人意愿包括什么。
In your opinion, does this kind of operation meet the donor's wishes? He Guoke: To judge whether it is against the will of the donor, the first step is to determine what the donor's intention is.
我认为从实践中来说，捐赠人的意愿是包括了捐赠人有权决定捐赠什么，捐赠的钱用于做什么，谁来接受捐赠，怎么使用捐赠财产和有权了解使用的效果(信息公开)等问题。
In practice, I think the donor's intention is to include such issues as what the donor has the right to donate, what the money is going to do, who will receive the donation, how to use the donated property, and the right to know the effect of the use (disclosure).
那么在本次新冠肺炎的防控当中，捐赠人向慈善总会捐赠的财产，他们的捐赠目的，还是比较明确的，就是用于新冠肺炎的防控，慈善总会是受赠主体，慈善总会应将受赠的财产用于疫情防控。
In the case of Pneumonia New Crown, the donor's donation to the charity, whose purpose is clear, is for the prevention and control of new crown pneumonia. The General Association of Charities is the grantee and should use the donated assets for disease control.
对于捐赠人来说，这就是他们理解的一个社会捐赠过程，而武汉市慈善总会根据指挥部要求，上缴市财政的行为，从某种程度上来说是违背了捐赠人对捐赠资金如何使用的意愿。
For donors, this is what they understand to be a social donation process, and Wuhan General Association of Philanthropy, in accordance with the command requirements, turned over the city's finances, in a way contrary to donors' willingness to use the donated funds.
比如，捐赠人向武汉市慈善总会捐赠1000元，慈善总会是先把资金给了财政，这个情况捐赠人并不知晓。
For example, if a donor donates 1000 yuan to the Wuhan General Association of Charity, the latter gives the money first, which the donor does not know.
有专家学者认为，湖北五家指定的慈善组织，实际上是政府在接受捐赠。
Some experts and scholars believe that the five designated charitable organizations in Hubei Province are actually receiving donations from the government.
但是我认为，在相关法律法规中，没有慈善组织代政府接受捐赠财产的依据，在通知公告中也没有看到政府接受捐赠或所接受捐赠要上缴财政的规定，只是提到捐赠款物由指挥部统一调配。
However, in my view, there is no basis in the relevant laws and regulations for charitable organizations to accept donations on behalf of the Government, nor is there any provision in the circular for the Government to accept donations or for accepting them to contribute financially, other than to mention that donations are centrally allocated by the command.
对于本人和广大捐赠人而言，其实并没有表达向政府捐赠的意愿，以及同意将捐赠财产上缴财政的做法。
For myself and the donor community, there is in fact no willingness to donate to the Government, as well as agreement to donate property to the financial practice.
另外，根据《公益事业捐赠法》第十一条 在发生自然灾害时或者境外捐赠人要求县级以上人民政府及其部门作为受赠人时，县级以上人民政府及其部门可以接受捐赠，并依照本法的有关规定对捐赠财产进行管理。
In addition, in accordance with Article 11 of the Law on Donations to Public Welfare Enterprises, when natural disasters occur or when foreign donors request the people's governments at or above the county level and their departments to act as grantees, the people's governments at or above the county level and their departments may accept donations and administer the donated property in accordance with the relevant provisions of this Law.
这里政府接受捐赠，也是按捐赠人的要求。
Here the government accepts the donation, also according to the donor's request.
夏彧歆：《慈善法》第五十一条 慈善组织的财产包括：(一)发起人捐赠、资助的创始财产;(二)募集的财产;(三)其他合法财产。
His name is Yu. His name is his name and he comes from his father, his name is his name, his name is his name and he comes from his father.
《慈善组织公开募捐管理办法》(民政部令第59号)第十九条 慈善组织应当加强对募得捐赠财产的管理，依据法律法规、章程规定和募捐方案使用捐赠财产。
Measures for the Administration of Public Collections by Charities (Order No. 59 of the Ministry of Civil Affairs) Article 19 Charitable organizations shall strengthen the administration of donated assets collected and use them in accordance with laws, regulations, rules and fund-raising schemes.
确需变更募捐方案规定的捐赠财产用途的，应当召开理事会进行审议，报其登记的民政部门备案，并向社会公开。
If it is really necessary to change the use of donated property as stipulated in the collection plan, the board of directors shall hold a deliberation and submit it to the civil affairs department registered with it for the record and make it public.
可以看出，武汉市慈善总会接收的款项属于社会捐赠，是慈善财产;武汉市慈善总会应当按照募捐方案使用捐赠财产，如果需要变更，须经法定程序。
As can be seen, the donations received by the Wuhan Municipal Charitable General Association are social donations and are charitable property; the Wuhan General Association of Philanthropy should use the donated property according to the fund-raising plan and go through legal procedures if necessary.
在武汉市有关部门发布的各类公告、武汉市慈善总会公布的募捐方案中，均未提到社会捐赠款项要上缴武汉市财政。
In the various announcements issued by the relevant departments in Wuhan and the fundraising plan announced by the Wuhan General Association of Charity, no mention was made of the need to hand over the social donation funds to Wuhan municipal finance.
如果将社会捐赠上缴市财政，这显然与在民政部门备案和总会公布的募捐方案不一致，更不符合上述法律规定及部门规章的精神。
If social donations are turned over to the municipal treasury, this is clearly not in keeping with the record of the civil administration and the fund-raising programme announced by the Federation, nor with the spirit of the above-mentioned legal provisions and departmental regulations.
再者，社会公众将款项捐给武汉市慈善总会，是对其的信任，是希望其严格按照《慈善法》等法律法规，依法合规有序用好社会爱心、及时支援抗疫一线;如果捐赠人知道募捐款项需要上缴市财政，他们很有可能就通过其他渠道捐赠、奉献爱心，而并不一定必须通过武汉市慈善总会。
In addition, the public donates funds to the Wuhan Municipal Charity Association in the hope that it will strictly abide by the Law and other laws and regulations, use social love in an orderly and timely manner, and provide timely support to the frontline of the epidemic.
这种做法，并不符合捐赠人意愿。
This is not in line with the donors' wishes.
第三，公众捐赠，其性质是社会公共资产、慈善财产;而上缴财政，则转变了财产性质。
Third, public donations, which are social public assets, charitable property in nature, and the surrender of financial resources, change the nature of property.
我们知道，财政款项，来源于国家税收、有关收费，以及其他法律法规确定的情形。
We know that financial contributions come from the state tax, relevant fees, and other legal and regulatory situations.
显然，社会捐赠款项并不属于上述范畴，不应当上缴财政。
It is clear that donations from the community do not fall within the above categories and should not be surrendered financially.
当然，我们也注意到，在各类公告中均有提及“由武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部统一调配使用市慈善总会社会捐赠款”的表述，但这并不能成为“社会捐赠上缴市财政”的法律依据。
Of course, we have also noted that in various announcements there are references to "the unified allocation and use of social donations by the Wuhan New Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command," but this does not constitute a legal basis for "social donations to the municipal treasury."
统一调配使用，没有问题，但方式很多，比如：武汉市慈善总会可以根据武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部的要求上报“非限定性”捐赠款项的使用方案和预算，由指挥部根据疫情防控整体情况审批;获批后，武汉市慈善总会直接将有关资助款项划拨相关单位，签订资助协议、提出资金使用要求及款项监督审计方案等，严格管理、追溯款项使用方式及途径，并依法做好信息公开、接受社会监督。
After approval, the Wuhan General Association of Philanthropy will directly transfer the related funds to relevant units, sign the funding agreement, put forward the requirements for the use of funds and the plan for auditing the funds, strictly manage and trace the ways and means of using the funds, and make information public and subject to public supervision according to law.
此种方式，合法合规、公信力高。
Such an approach is legitimate and credible.
第四，如果捐赠款项上缴市财政，我不知道在这种情况下，有关社会组织如何依法进行、依规做好信息公开?若公布社会捐赠上缴市财政，这与募捐方案及有关规定不符;若公布社会捐赠直接拨付、资助有关机构，这又与实际情况不符。
Fourth, if the donation is turned over to the municipal treasury, I do not know how the relevant social organizations will proceed according to the law and make the information public according to the rules. If the public donation is released to the municipal treasury, it is not in line with the collection plan and the relevant regulations.
不得而知。
Not known.
《公益时报》：从现有的公开资料显示，没有查到相关内容的程序性解释或公开说明。
The pro bono Times: According to the publicly available information, no procedural explanation or public statement of the content was found.
如果有必要且一定要这么操作，合法合规的程序应该是怎样的?应参照哪些相关法律条款?何国科：从尊重捐赠人的角度来说，捐赠人应当是有知情权的，如果必须上缴财政，应当事先告知捐赠人，已经上缴市财政的，也应当履行信息公开义务，告知捐赠人捐赠款项的使用，应当依照《公益事业捐赠法》和《慈善法》的要求履行信息公开义务，而不是仅告知捐赠人已经上缴财政就结束了。
If it is necessary and necessary to do so, what should be the procedures for legal compliance? What are the relevant legal provisions? HONG Ke: From the perspective of respecting donors, donors should be informed in advance that they have paid in financial resources and that the use of donations should be made in accordance with the Law on Donations to Public Welfare Enterprises and the Law on Charity.
财政怎么使用的，用做什么，用了多少?这些信息也应当披露。
How finance is used, what it is used for, and how much it is spent? This information should also be disclosed.
夏彧歆：《公益事业捐赠法》第五条 捐赠财产的使用应当尊重捐赠人的意愿，符合公益目的，不得将捐赠财产挪作他用。
Xia Din: Article 5 The use of donated property respects the wishes of the donor, serves a public interest purpose and does not permit the diversion of donated property.
《慈善法》第五十二条 慈善组织的财产应当根据章程和捐赠协议的规定全部用于慈善目的，不得在发起人、捐赠人以及慈善组织成员中分配。
Article 52 The property of a charitable organization shall be used exclusively for charitable purposes in accordance with the articles of association and the provisions of the donation agreement, and shall not be distributed among the sponsors, donors or members of charitable organizations.
任何组织和个人不得私分、挪用、截留或者侵占慈善财产。
No organization or individual may privately divide, misappropriate, retain or encroach upon charitable property.
综上，有关法律并未授权政府部门要求有关机构将社会捐赠财产上缴财政统一调配。
Above all, the relevant laws do not authorize government departments to request the relevant agencies to turn over socially donated property to fiscal consolidation.
显然，现在的做法缺乏法律基础和法律依据。
Clearly, the current practice lacks a legal basis and a legal basis.
当然，在当前特殊情况下，为更好地开展疫情防控和抗击工作，对政府部门出台一些特殊政策，应该理解并支持;但这有一个前提，就是必须依法行政。
Of course, under the current special circumstances, special policies for government departments should be understood and supported in order to better control and combat the epidemic, but this presupposes that the administration of justice is required.
如果武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部认为有必要将社会捐赠款项上缴市财政统一调配使用，应当按照有关程序，依法提请全国人大常委会在相关法律框架下授权;经授权后，方可执行，且要及时向社会公示。
If the Wuhan New Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command deems it necessary to turn over the social donation funds to the municipal treasury for unified use, it shall, in accordance with the relevant procedures, submit to the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress for authorization under the relevant legal framework.
显然，现在这个程序和授权，是缺失的;且武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部和有关部门也没有解释、公示此种做法的法律依据。
Obviously, the current procedure and authorization are missing, and the Wuhan New Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command and relevant departments have not explained and made public the legal basis for such a practice.
《公益时报》：对于此事涉及的相关部门，你的法律建议是什么?何国科：我认为社会捐赠财产由指挥部统一调配这个没有问题，但对于上缴财政的行为不能理解。
What is your legal proposal for the relevant departments involved in this matter? He Guoke: I don't think there is any problem for the social donation to be unified by the headquarters, but I can't understand the act of handing in the money.
指挥部根据新冠肺炎防控实际情况需求，要求慈善总会将社会捐赠财产拨付给相关主体，慈善总会按照指挥部要求执行，并向社会公示，这个不存在任何法律障碍，不知道上缴市财政的必要性在于什么地方?是政府对慈善总会的不信任，还是慈善总会对用好社会捐赠没有信心?对于上缴市财政的社会捐赠资金，更是应该做好信息披露，不能说上缴财政了，慈善组织也好、政府也好，其信息公开相关义务就结束了。
According to the actual situation of New Crown Pneumonia, the command requires the General Association of Charities to transfer social donation property to the relevant subjects.
夏彧歆：2月10日，为促进新冠肺炎疫情防控工作依法有序开展，全国人大常委会法制工作委员会相关室负责人，就疫情防控中社会普遍关心的法律问题进行了解答。
Xia Yu: On 10 February, to make sure that the work of preventing and controlling the new crown pneumonia is carried out in an orderly and legal manner, the head of the Legal Work Committee of the Standing Committee of the National People's Congress answers legal questions that are of general interest to society in preventing and controlling the disease.
全国人大常委会法工委社会法室主任郭林茂就“公益慈善捐赠活动”，依据《公益事业捐赠法》《慈善法》《红十字会法》等法律，从“鼓励捐赠、公开透明、及时高效、公平合理、接受监督、依法追责”等六个方面进行阐述，并强调：“依法治国要求把国家各项事业纳入法治轨道，更需要全社会都要依法行事。
Guo Linmao, director of the Social Law Office of the Standing Committee of the NPC Standing Committee, elaborated on "charitable activities of public benefit" and other laws, including "encouraging donation, transparency, timely and efficient, fairness, supervision and legal accountability."
所以，具有慈心善行的捐赠人要合法捐赠，捐赠物品要符合安全、卫生、环保等标准，信守诺言;红十字会、各类慈善组织要依法及时高效、公平合理分配受赠款物，无愧捐赠人，无愧受益人;政府有关部门要对捐赠款物使用情况依法严格监督，对党负责，对人民负责。
The Red Cross Society and all kinds of charitable organizations should distribute the donations in a timely, efficient and fair manner, with clear conscience as beneficiaries. The relevant government departments should strictly supervise the use of donations in accordance with the law, be accountable to the Party and be accountable to the people.
同时，也欢迎全社会对公益慈善捐赠活动进行监督，为中国公益慈善事业的发展作一份贡献。
At the same time, the whole society is welcome to supervise the charitable activities of public welfare and make a contribution to the development of public charity in China.
” 我认为，在当前疫情防控和抗击的关键时期，各级党委、政府应当按照《慈善法》《公益事业捐赠法》等法律法规和与其配套的部门规章、规范性文件等，依法建立协调机制，提供需求信息，及时有序引导开展募捐和救助活动，并对捐赠款物使用情况依法严格监督;对目前无法律授权而又必须特殊处理的紧急情况，应当依法获得授权。
"I believe that in the current critical period of epidemic prevention, control and resistance, Party committees and governments at all levels should, in accordance with the Law on Charity, the Law on Donations to Public Welfare Enterprises and their corresponding departmental rules and normative documents, establish coordination mechanisms, provide demand information, guide fund-raising and rescue activities in a timely and orderly manner and strictly supervise the use of donations.
这才是“依法治国、依法行政”的落实和体现。
This is the "rule of law, administration by law" implementation and embodiment.
